data.title: Actor Michael Caine, 85, On His Long Career: 'The Alternative Was A Factory'
data.meta_description: From the title heartthrob in Alfie to the fatherly butler of the Batman franchise, the actor has been filling movie screens for a half-century. His new memoir is Blowing The Bloody Doors Off.
